WorldTree.Name: World

WorldTree.LastScript:
var cylRadius = 75.0 //mm;
  var cylLength = 200.0//mm;
  var cylDist   = 250.0 //mm;

  var colSizeX  = 400.0 //mm; // along the beam
  var colSizeY  = 500.0 //mm; // width
  var colSizeZ  = 200.0 //mm; // height

  var septa     = 2.4 //mm;
  var aperture  = 5.1 //mm;
  var pitch     = septa + aperture;

  var sciSizeX  = 2.0 //mm; // should be < 0.5*aperture !
  var sciSizeZ  = 30.0 //mm;
  var tapeX     = (aperture - 2.0 * sciSizeX) * 0.25
  tapeX
  core.abort(tapeX)
  
  var teflonTop = 0.2 //mm - teflon layer on top of the scintillator

  var    numEl     =  math.floor(colSizeX / pitch)
  core.print("Number of scintillators: "+ numEl*2)
  
  RemoveAllExceptWorld()

  Cylinder( "pmma", 2.0*cylRadius, cylLength, 5, "World", 0+0.5*cylLength, 0, 0.5*colSizeZ + cylDist, 90,90,0)
  SetLine( "pmma",  2,  1,  1 )

  var scintPos = []
  for (var iCol = 0; iCol<=numEl; iCol++)
  {
      var offset = iCol*pitch
      
      Box("ColBlade"+iCol, septa, colSizeY, colSizeZ, 1, "World", offset,0,0,   0,0,0)
      SetLine("ColBlade"+iCol, 4,1,1)
      
      if (iCol == numEl) break
      
      Box("Teflon"+iCol, aperture, colSizeY, sciSizeZ+teflonTop, 4, "World", offset + 0.5*pitch,0,-0.5*colSizeZ + 0.5*sciSizeZ + 0.5*teflonTop,   0,0,0)
      SetLine("Teflon"+iCol, 5,1,1)

      var posLeft  = -tapeX - 0.5*sciSizeX
      var posRight =  tapeX + 0.5*sciSizeX
      scintPos.push(offset + 0.5*pitch + posLeft)
      scintPos.push(offset + 0.5*pitch + posRight)
      
      Box("Scint"+iCol*2, sciSizeX, colSizeY, sciSizeZ, 3, "Teflon"+iCol, posLeft,0,-0.5*teflonTop,   0,0,0)
      SetLine("Scint"+iCol*2, 7,1,1)
      
      Box("Scint"+(iCol*2+1), sciSizeX, colSizeY, sciSizeZ, 3, "Teflon"+iCol, posRight,0,-0.5*teflonTop,   0,0,0)
      SetLine("Scint"+(iCol*2+1), 7,1,1)

  }
